fields.value: REPLICATION DATA FOR: Bootstrap Methods for Inference in the Parks Model

dsDescriptionValue.value: This dataset contains all the materials needed to reproduce the results in "Bootstrap Methods for Inference in the Parks Model". Please read the README document first. The results were obtained using SAS/IML software, and the files consist of SAS data sets and SAS programs.
